      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "STARLET EDITION (4) jumped from out wide and was game in defeat last start when a 0.8 lengths second (19.83) behind Runaway Merv at this track. Key chance in this line up. SHAKA GOES BANG (7) finished third last time (20.00) at this track after winning at his previous two outings. Form at the trip sound including 14 wins. Boxed out wide but fast beginner who can clear and cross early. Expecting another good run. MINH JACK (2) settled close the lead but was checked in the run and turned spotting a start, winding up strongly to place (19.98) at this track over 342m in a Other. Safe beginner and drawn well close to the inside. Expected to feature. VICTA BOB (1) missed the placings here most recently but can sneak into the finish with the right run.",
